@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<style>
    .privacy-policy-container {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
        gap: 20px;
    }

    .column {
        padding: 20px;
    }
</style>

<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

<div class="privacy-policy-container">
    <div class="column">
        <h2>Purpose of the Website</h2>
        <p>This website is designed as a second-year integrated project focused on quality assurance, project management, and client-focused digital solutions. It aims to demonstrate the knowledge and skills developed through coursework in a practical, real-world scenario.</p>

        <h2>How the Website Works</h2>
        <p>Users can create accounts to access a dashboard with tools related to project management, quality assurance, and team collaboration.</p>
        <p>The website provides options for tracking project milestones, assessing task completion, and storing important documents.</p>
        <p>It utilizes secure data handling practices to protect user information, ensuring that all personal and project-related data remain confidential and are processed per industry standards.</p>

        <h2>Collection and Use of Personal Information</h2>
        <p>The website collects personal information such as names, email addresses, and project data for account creation and personalized access to project tools.</p>
        <p>All collected data is used exclusively for providing access to the platform's features, improving user experience, and ensuring secure access to project-related information.</p>
        <p>The website does not share personal information with third parties without user consent unless required by law.</p>

        
    </div>

    <div class="column">
        <h2>Functionality of the Website</h2>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>User Authentication</strong>: Users must create accounts or log in to access certain features of the website, ensuring security and personalization.</li>
            <li><strong>Project Management Tools</strong>: Features that allow users to set milestones, track progress, and manage project timelines.</li>
            <li><strong>Quality Assurance Tracking</strong>: Tools to assess and ensure the quality of ongoing projects, providing checkpoints and evaluation criteria.</li>
            <li><strong>Data Storage and Retrieval</strong>: Secure storage for project-related files, documents, and notes, accessible only to authenticated users.</li>
            <li><strong>Collaboration Features</strong>: Options for team members to communicate, leave feedback, and update the status of various tasks.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>User Rights</h2>
        <p>Users have the right to access, update, and delete their personal information stored on the website.</p>
        <p>They can request a copy of their data or contact support for data-related queries.</p>

        <h2>Security Measures</h2>
        <p>The website implements advanced security measures to protect user data, including encryption, regular security audits, and restricted access to sensitive information.</p>
        <p>Users are encouraged to follow best practices for password security to protect their accounts from unauthorized access.</p>

        <h2>Changes to Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>The website may update its privacy policy periodically to comply with legal standards or improve transparency. Users will be notified of any significant changes.</p>
    </div>
</div>